{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_06_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 1話 すみれの武者修行",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "聞いて下さい、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please listen‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.5278535001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.770090731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、千紗さん、こころちゃん、すずちゃんと\n今度一緒にユニットを組むことになったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ Chisa-san‚ Kokoro-chan‚ Suzu-chan‚ and I\nare going to form a unit together next time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.6498183807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、橋本さんから聞いてるよ\nみんなで合宿して、企画を考えたんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I've heard from Hashimoto-san.\nYou all stayed together for training and brainstorming‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.0999999841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです、合宿すっごく楽しかったです！\nそれで、私がセンターに任命されまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ exactly! The training camp was so much fun!\nAnd then‚ I was appointed as the center…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "センターと言えば瑠依ちゃん……演劇なら座長……\nそんな責任重大な役割、私に務まるでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to the center‚ it's usually Rui-chan… if it's a play‚ she's the lead…\nWill I be able to handle such a significant responsibility…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.7771471899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれなら、きっと大丈夫だよ\nライブを観るのを、俺も楽しみにしてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's you‚ Sumire‚ I'm sure you'll be fine.\nI'm also looking forward to watching the live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.5769177994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも来てくれるんですか？\n……これは、ますます責任重大になってきましたね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will you come too‚ {user}-san?\n…This is becoming even more of a responsibility!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2627002956
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブに向けて練習を開始した数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later from practice for the live performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3293669623,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.6666665999965,
          "startTime": 58.6960336289
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　お疲れ様です、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Thank you for your hard work‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すみれもお疲れ様\nさすが、気合いが入ってるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You too‚ Sumire.\nSeems like you're fired up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.533335352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですけど……実は……\nあ、でも今回はさとみさんに相談した方がいいのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ but… actually…\nAh‚ but maybe I should consult with Hashimoto-san about this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8666686853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "大事なことは、橋本さんとみんなに相談するべきだけど\n話を聞くくらいなら、俺も力になるぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Important matters should be discussed with Hashimoto-san and everyone‚\nbut if you just want to talk‚ I can lend an ear too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.533335352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……本当ですか？\nじゃあ、ちょっとだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Really?\nThen‚ just a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9000020187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "私、いつも瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんと一緒ですし\n子役の頃も先輩達が沢山いましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm always with Rui-chan and Yu-chan.\nEven when I was a child actor‚ I had many seniors‚ and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0666742802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "他のみんなに頼ってばっかりで\n自分が引っ張らないと、ってことがなかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always relied on others‚\nso I never had to take the lead myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0333409469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "頼る相手がいると、つい甘えちゃうもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you have someone to rely on‚ you tend to lean on them easily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7724843425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい……でも今回は、私がセンターですから\nユニットのコンセプトを――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… but this time‚ I'm the center.\nFor the unit's concept‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3333389123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "『みんなの素の魅力』を引き出すためにも\n私が、みんなを引っ張らないといけないなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to bring out 'everyone's natural charm'\nI have to lead everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4666691939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは\n星見プロのみんなから、頼りにされてますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you know {user}-san‚\neveryone at Hoshimi Prods relies on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8051077288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "私もそんな風になるには、どうしたらいいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do to become like that too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.630330221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺だって日々勉強中だよ\n事務所に入った頃は、三枝さんに毎日怒られてたしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm still learning every day.\nWhen I first joined the agency‚ I was scolded by Saegusa-san every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0999923546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2601948183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれがお世話になった先輩も、きっとそうだと思うぞ\nみんな誰かに教わりながら、少しずつ覚えるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure even the seniors Sumire's relied on have been through that.\nEveryone learns little by little while being taught by someone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4666590213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "すみれも、まずは他の人のやり方を見るのがいいかもな\n理想の、目標にしたいセンターがいるなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ maybe it's best for you to start by observing how others do it.\nIf there's a center you want to emulate‚ someone you aspire to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.7999893028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "それはもちろん、瑠依ちゃんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ that's Rui-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.5313903015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "あんな風に、堂々と真ん中に立って\n他のみんなを引っ張っていけたらなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to stand confidently in the center like her\nand lead everyone just like she does.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.2666559695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。まず瑠依に話を聞いてみるのが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Maybe you should start by talking to Rui…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.1848820369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。いつも瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんに頼ってますけど\n今回は自分の力で頑張ってみたいんです",
      "translations": {
