      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。瑠依ちゃんは練習の鬼ですから\n私も他のみんなより沢山練習しなくちゃって",
      "translations": {
