      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr023.m4a",
      "text": "それに、練習が終わった後は\n瑠依ちゃんを追いかけないといけないので",
